snippet.title: World-Splitter [Switch/PS4/XOne/PC] Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
World-Splitter is a puzzle/platformer where you complete stages by positioning and rotating dimension rifts that separate two vibrant, beautifully animated worlds.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/14918/

World-Splitter will launch on PS4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch and PC (Steam) April 21 for $19.99.
